in a river of tears ♪

171
00:13:40,166 --> 00:13:44,166
♪ Lord,
send down an angel ♪

172
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,767
♪ to carry me across ♪

173
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:50,266
♪ 'cause I can't seem
